text: Team Betta Electrical may refer to these teams that competed in the V8 Supercars championship with Betta Electrical as title sponsor: *John Faulkner Racing: 1996 - 1998 *Briggs Motor Sport: 2002 - 2003 *Paul Weel Racing: 2002 *Triple Eight Race Engineering: 2004 - 2006
title: Team Betta Electrical
